      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "I think the problem is in `AddCoin`: AFAICT `cachedCoinsUsage` is decreased also in the case when we throw `std::logic_error(\"Attempted to overwrite an unspent coin (when possible_overwrite is false)\")`.\r\n\r\nThis sequence triggers the problem:\r\n1. A successful `AddCoin(â¦, â¦, false)` call\r\n1. A failed `AddCoin(â¦, â¦, false)` call (`std::logic_error`)\r\n1. A `AddCoin(â¦, â¦, false)` call\r\n\r\nLet me know if further details are needed.\r\n\r\n",
